		.g-s-6.post
			:markdown
				The type on this website is set in [Tiempos](https://klim.co.nz/collections/tiempos/ "Tiempos, by Klim Type Foundry") and [Söhne](https://klim.co.nz/collections/soehne/ "Söhne, by Klim Type Foundry"), both from the [Klim Type Foundry](https://klim.co.nz/ "Klim Type Foundry") in New Zealand. 

				Article headlines and page titles are set in Tiempos Headline. Body text is set in Tiempos Text.  I chose Tiempos for it’s roots in Times New Roman and for its associations with newspaper design. 
			
				Supporting headings, navigation and some lists are set in Söhne Buch. I chose Söhne for its feeling of ubiquity, it's evident craftsmanship, and for it’s association with my adopted home of New York. 
				
				You can read loving descriptions of the [development of Tiempos](https://klim.co.nz/blog/tiempos-design-information/ "Tiempos design information") and the [development of Söhne](https://klim.co.nz/blog/soehne-design-information/ "Söhne design information") on the Klim blog. 
				
				
